 255);\">据《印度时报》1月20日报道，索尼公司和三星电子已分别在印度裁剪了约150名高管人员，这主要是由于过去两个月销售不景气，而且中国公司也在抢夺智能手机市场，竞争日趋激烈。据四位匿名的行业内高管表示，索尼印度公司给员工提供了自愿离职的机会，而印度最大的手机销售商三星电子则直接要求地区市场支持部和售后服务部的中层管理人员主动离职，此举主要是为了降低公司成本。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_172845_528.jpg\" alt=\"中国厂商太猛， 索尼三星印度被逼裁员\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">报道称，索尼印度公司的市场份额已由两年前的6-7%下降至1%，如今公司正在缩减手机业务规模，这势必会导致裁员。经公司的一位发言人证实，索尼公司向手机部门的长期雇员提供了虚拟参考站技术(VRS)，此举有望在公司转战高端智能手机市场时优化资源配置。公司还打算通过精简运营过程和提高运作效率，建立一个稳定的业务基础。发言人还补充说，消费者可以继续方便快捷地购买公司的产品。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">三星电子在排灯节之前就已解雇250名员工，现在已着手缩减市场销售部门的多层管理结构。三星印度公司总裁在最近的国际消费电子展(CES 2016)上也谈及了公司2015年低于预期的增长速度和成本削减措施，包括裁员。但是三星电子西南亚地区的发言人则表示，这些关于裁员的消息是莫须有的。</p>\n		    	<!-- 编辑区域 -->\n		    ','2016-03-02 14:54:01',1,'01',1,33,'关键词1,关键词2,关键词3','','','http://sourceimg-10021396.image.myqcloud.com/9641dad3-28b0-420f-9fdc-d2bf58df3e24'),(25,2,'印度最大电商Flipkart谈Win10 UWP应用开发历程','<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">上周，印度最大电商公司Flipkart（网上购物网站）推出了他们的<a class=\"s_tag\" href=\"http://win10.ithome.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: text;\">Win10</a>&nbsp;UWP客户端，适配<a class=\"s_tag\" href=\"http://win10.ithome.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: text;\">Windows10</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>PC和<a class=\"s_tag\" href=\"http://win10.ithome.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: text;\">Win10 Mobile</a>平台，这次更新也吸引了大量用户涌入。今天，这款Win10通用应用背后开发团队分享了开发体验。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_181436_374.jpg\" alt=\"印度最大电商Flipkart谈Win10 UWP应用开发历程\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">通常产品的开发路线首先是分析市场，查找差距弥补，撰写产品需求文档、讨论/头脑风暴，进行包装，然后是设计和开发。它开始于试验，逐步成为优先级项目。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">团队中有两名设计人员负责，面临挑战是创建响应式应用同时保证后台数据呈现商业逻辑进行。当项目开始时，UWP还是新的概念，几乎没有其他应用进行参考和功能性指导。此外，Flipkart是非常复杂应用，用户基数很大。其风险很高而不能犯错。用户并不清楚这样应用面临的情况。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">Flipkart</strong>下载（美国区），<a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/apps/flipkart/9wzdncrfj356\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: pointer;\">点此链接</a>或使用玩应用App（<a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/zh-cn/store/Apps/%E7%8E%A9%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/9WZDNCRDKXBV\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: pointer;\">下载链接</a>）扫描下列二维码：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_182014_997.jpg\" alt=\"印度最大电商Flipkart谈Win10 UWP应用开发历程\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_182014_997.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p>','2016-01-21 18:44:19',1,'01',1,18,NULL,NULL,NULL,'http://sourceimg-10021396.image.myqcloud.com/680e05d2-6e8b-4dc0-9e9a-4731d3a8cf60'),(27,1,'A站和B站的宅文化究竟有什么不同？','\n		    	<!-- 编辑区域 -->\n		    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">作为新一代年轻宅男宅女聚集地的弹幕视频网站AcFun（A站）和Bilibili（B站），将曾经更为小众的二次元“宅文化”进一步展现在大众面前，就算你没有专门去看那些动画、漫画和游戏，但一定也听过“叶良辰”和“赵日天”的故事。没错，赵日天这一根本不存在的人物着实在2015年火了一把。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而最近AcFun（以下简称A站）正式公布，<a href=\"http://www.ithome.com/html/it/200900.htm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: pointer;\">获得了软银中国的6000万美元A+轮投资</a>，而这轮融资将用于品牌推广和产品完善。同时宣布：莫然出任公司CEO，原CEO孙旻出任总裁。在去年A站就已经获得由优酷土豆领投的5000万美元投资。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但在年轻人的移动社交生活中占比这样大的“二次元”世界是怎么样，也许还有更多的人表示不能理解。宅男宅女也不仅仅再是一个小众群体，如你所见当90后们长大成为各行各业做争夺的受众群体，其代表的“宅文化”也正如潮涨之势袭来。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">内容较量下的A站、B站看的到底什么？</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">用一个字概括就是：<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">宅</strong>，当“宅”成为一种文化形态，用户对他们则产生了更多期待。<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">“二次元”文化作为它们无数用户背后的力量源泉。从现有状况来看，B站仍在ACG（动画、漫画和游戏）的内容上发力：各种独播新番内容轮流上线，话题一般围绕“宅基腐”，而相比之下的A站则更倾向于带有二次元色彩的三次元内容，以游戏为特色</strong>。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_160958_930.jpg\" alt=\"A站和B站的宅文化究竟有什么不同？\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">呆萌下的B站</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">即使在A站新番更新较少之下，它仍然拥有一批黏性较高的用户群体，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">也很难说这其实是一批更为忠实的“资深宅”</strong>。用户自身的鲜明特点也从A站的文章区和评论区看出来：当“御宅族”发表一些基于二次元世界观的三次元观察，文章中的指点江山、评论区高谈阔论，使得不少宅梗诞生。比如跟着“叶良辰”重新火了一把的“赵日天”，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">最先便是在A站匿名版里诞生，UP主“一大碗雪橇”发布在《老子名叫赵日天》</strong>，随后曾有妖气上连载的唐小云的《断罪小学》漫画上迅速蹿红，进而流行于网络。但也因此将讨论范围锁定在评论区内，一定程度上形成内容孤岛。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">所以，什么人在看A站和B站？</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_160959_165.jpg\" alt=\"A站和B站的宅文化究竟有什么不同？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_160959_165.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在两者都同时拥有高度粘性用户的同时，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">A站的人群普遍比B站大3至5岁</strong><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">。这个年龄差也决定了A站具有更强的社会属性，而B站拥有更多学生党</strong>，也就不难理解在内容上A站的视频内容在二次元的基础上慢慢扩散至三次元的社会属性上。但“宅”性依旧，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">A站则掌握更多拥有“情怀”的御宅群体</strong>。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虽同为弹幕网站，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">B站弹幕的活跃程度明显多于A站，重复和无意义的也多</strong>，但被概括为“呆萌”群体的B站用户乐此不疲。内容尽管是重点与用户入口，但让更多A站老用户迷恋的却是让其引以为豪的文章区和评论区。在某种层面上来看，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">在AcFuns上人们关注的重点也许不是内容本身，更是以一种特殊环境下所获得的满足感</strong>。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_160959_331.jpg\" alt=\"A站和B站的宅文化究竟有什么不同？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_160959_331.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A站文章区</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网络上关于AcFun和Bilibili的争论仍然在一直进行着，其实不论你是这两者之中哪个网站的死忠粉都好<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">，同为二次元弹幕网站的他们在经过几年的发展后在网友的高度自制下形成如今看起来具有鲜明特色风格的网站，二次元也好三次元也罢可以找到自己身心上的“精神食粮”就足够了吧</strong>。</p>','2016-03-02 14:46:11',1,'10',1,97,'关键词1,关键词2,关键词3','','','http://sourceimg-10021396.image.myqcloud.com/c8c980b4-4036-46ef-817e-810dc3366e08'),(28,1,'中国联通部分客户端被曝低级Bug：无密码随便登陆','\n		    	<!-- 编辑区域 -->\n		    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">运营商相关的产品漏洞已经数见不鲜了，此前我们还报道过<a href=\"http://www.ithome.com/html/it/197934.htm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: pointer;\">三大运营商流量计费系统的漏洞</a>，不过那个比较隐蔽，而今天乌云漏洞平台曝光的有关中国联通部分客户端的Bug就比较低级了，一旦被黑客发现，会轻易对用户会造成严重损失。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_181643_624.jpg\" alt=\"中国联通部分客户端被曝低级Bug：无密码随便登陆\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根据漏洞发现者恶人毛透露，中国联通的沃流量、沃邮箱等<a class=\"s_tag\" href=\"http://android.ithome.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: text;\">Android</a>客户端可能被用户免密码登陆，主要原因出在客户端本身的一键登录功能。无需输入密码，可以看出原理是利用验证手机SIM卡是否有效的方式实现的，于是该作者突发奇想，如果改变SIM卡手机号会怎么样？</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_181636_247.png\" alt=\"中国联通部分客户端被曝低级Bug：无密码随便登陆\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_181636_247.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_181749_689.png\" alt=\"中国联通部分客户端被曝低级Bug：无密码随便登陆\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_181749_689.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">于是该发现者利用xposed+改号软件，将SIM卡手机号码改成任意号码，修改后同样能通过验证，比较简单。像18577777777，18566666666这样的号码都能登陆。并且注册账号时候必须注册的邮箱也能成功同步过来，包含历史邮件，这样，就会对其他用户造成不可估量的损失了。而且经验证，完全可以通过抓包抓取到邮箱的POP3密码。<br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_181636_588.png\" alt=\"中国联通部分客户端被曝低级Bug：无密码随便登陆\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_181636_588.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">可以看出整个过程唯一的技术手段就是更改SIM卡手机号，而这通过软件手段也可以简单实现，显然联通方面对客户端的意见登陆功能并没有做足够的安全验证措施，属于明显的低级Bug。</p>','2016-03-02 14:53:22',1,'00',1,62,'关键词1,关键词2,关键词3','','','http://sourceimg-10021396.image.myqcloud.com/75966ef1-0410-4d4e-b31c-597279e38351'),(29,1,'Wii U《超级马里奥制造》登陆Win10：就靠Cemu模拟器','<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">模拟器是游戏跨平台运行的利器，有效解决了某些用户无法利用手头设备玩其他平台游戏的问题。虽然很多时候在新平台上模拟的运行环境并不理想，但这并没有影响玩家和模拟器开发者的热情。最近，Wii U平台热门游戏《超级马里奥制造（Super Mario Maker）》被Cemu 1.3.0请到了<a class=\"s_tag\" href=\"http://www.win7china.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: text;\">Win7</a>/<a class=\"s_tag\" href=\"http://win8.ithome.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: text;\">Win8.1</a>/<a class=\"s_tag\" href=\"http://win10.ithome.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: text;\">Win10</a>平台，开发者发布了相关视频介绍。<br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_152305_982.jpg\" alt=\"Wii U《超级马里奥制造》登陆Win10：就靠Cemu模拟器\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从视频中可以看到，这款模拟器在<a class=\"s_tag\" href=\"http://win10.ithome.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: text;\">Windows10</a>预览版11082上的效果还是不错的，测试者用鼠标就可以完成超级马里奥关卡的设计，整个过程非常流畅。另外，在IT之家实际测试中，在Win10预览版11099中首次打开模拟器时，系统会提示缺少MSVCP.DLL文件和MSVCR.DLL文件，这是由于系统运行库不完整所致，你可以单独补齐这两个文件，也可以尝试安装相关微软运行库，<a href=\"http://mofang.ruanmei.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: pointer;\">软媒魔方</a>（<a href=\"http://down.ruanmei.com/tweakcube/partner/pcmastersetup_u143.exe\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: pointer;\">点击下载</a>）的软件管家中有所有运行库文件可供选择。</p>','2016-01-21 18:53:31',1,'00',1,8,NULL,NULL,NULL,'http://sourceimg-10021396.image.myqcloud.com/680e05d2-6e8b-4dc0-9e9a-4731d3a8cf60'),(30,1,'谷歌Google Play首进中国，它将如何更接地气？','<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Google Play将重回中国的消息越来越多，也越来越有可靠性了。最近一组Google Play的app截图又流传在网上，<a href=\"http://www.ithome.com/html/it/202255.htm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: pointer;\">在软件版本号中出现了“CHINA”的字样</a>，看来Google Play将有中国定制版的真实性又增加了。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_163313_882.jpg\" alt=\"谷歌Google Play首进中国，它将如何更接地气？\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">同时在支付方式里，截图中还出现了支付宝的选项，另外也支持信用卡与借记卡支付。看来中国版的Google Play还挺接地气的，知道中国用户都喜欢使用支付宝这类的移动支付app来网上购物，如果有微信支付那就更好了。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_163301_735.jpg\" alt=\"谷歌Google Play首进中国，它将如何更接地气？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_163301_735.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">既然Google Play为了进中国，已经在本地化上开始下功夫，那我们也不妨预测下Google Play中国版的一些本地化改变，与国际版Google Play会有什么不同呢？</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">1.使用与国际版Google Play相独立的账号是一定的了</strong>。注册邮箱应该不会强制为Gmail，像QQ邮箱之类的个人邮箱也可以注册。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">2.应用数量肯定不如国际版Google Play那么丰富，该屏蔽的软件还是会屏蔽，不会给你们留任何机会的</strong>。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">3.谷歌可能做不到说服所有国产Android厂商都默认内置Google Play</strong>，毕竟他们早已发展自己的应用商店。中国版Google Play可能以app的形式在各大应用商店上架，但这是不是会形成竞争关系而遭到封杀就不好说了。至于国外的Android厂商，谷歌应该还是有点话语权的吧。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">4.国际版Google Play能够根据用户的所在位置，自动切换语言和地区，但中国版Google Play应该不具备这样的功能</strong>吧，语言和地区都是默认中国大陆，应该也算是一个单独的app。所以有没有可能在一台手机上同时存在国际版Google Play与中国版Google Play呢？可能性应该还蛮大的吧。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">5.国际版Google Play并不只是应用商店</strong>，它还兼职卖电影、卖电子书、卖音乐。当然，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">中国版Google Play想必只是一个纯粹的应用商店</strong>吧，至于后面谷歌会不会通过谈判的方式引入电影音乐的在线购买功能，也不是完全没有可能。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">6.Google Play的最大优点在于，不会有盗版，也不有恶意的广告植入</strong>。虽然不能说完全没有恶意软件，但相信在英明的审核机制下中国版Google Play将会做到纯净无污染吧。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">7.至于app的更新速度，能否与国际版Google Play同步？这是个未知数</strong>。同步与相差一段时间的可能性都有，毕竟是中国特别版。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有消息称，中国版Google Play最早可能会在3月正式进入中国。到那时，就可以和各大国内应用商店说拜拜了。Google Play一生推，从不用第三方应用商店。</p>','2016-01-21 18:54:14',1,'00',1,15,NULL,NULL,NULL,'http://sourceimg-10021396.image.myqcloud.com/680e05d2-6e8b-4dc0-9e9a-4731d3a8cf60'),(31,2,'最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？','<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">昨日（1月20日）“大寒”节气的到来，一瞬间消弭了南北方的分歧，无分彼此，分分钟变“速冻粽子”下锅。中央气象台说南方七省将迎来大到暴雪，南方的小伙伴纷纷表示“妈妈再也不用担心我被嘲笑没见过雪了”。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这时，北方的小伙伴微微一笑，轻轻哼起，“你在南方的艳阳里，大雪纷飞/我在北方的寒夜里，四季如春”。到这终于明白了，敢情马頔这首《南山南》是在讴歌暖气啊，而且在不经意间还放了个群嘲技能。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151003_321.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是马啪啪可能不知道，为了他能在寒夜里唱四季如春，古代人民可是同寒魔进行了长期艰苦卓绝的斗争，才发明出暖气这个伟大神器。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">粗犷的火炕系列</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151004_509.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151004_509.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">▲火塘文化。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">火塘是比较原始的取暖方式，也就比围个火堆稍微好一点，在半坡、姜寨等遗址中就有。半坡人、姜寨人在房屋内用土铺成个一米见方的土块，上面垒起石头，用于架锅烧饭，晚上则可以烤火取暖。直到现在，在中国南方如普米族、纳西族、白族、傣族等少数民族中，仍然在使用火塘，因为在这些人群中，火塘已经超越单纯的工具意义，具有了家族关系和仪式的象征意义。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151004_556.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151004_556.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">▲</strong>南方少数民族的火塘除了实用功能外，更兼有社会、文化和宗教等意涵。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">火墙则比火塘要先进了许多。在秦长乐宫遗址发现的火墙是用两块筒瓦相扣，做成管道，包于墙内，与灶相通。明清更为彻底，干脆将房屋的墙壁砌成空心，墙下挖有火道，添火的炭口一般设于房外。为使热力循环通畅，火道的尽头设有气孔，烟气由台基下出气口排出。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">火炕可以简单理解为将火墙横过来平置，尤其流行于北方少数民族。比如西汉苏武在匈奴牧羊19年，就是靠火炕熬过极北苦寒的。而在《三朝北盟会编》记载，女真人的居室必有火炕，甚至金太祖完颜阿骨打和部落首领议事都是在炕上。但火炕一般有两个灶，做饭的锅灶不与炕在同一房间，卧室内炕另有一个专为加热的灶，这种形制至今仍在东北农村广泛使用。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">优雅的温调房</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151004_695.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151004_695.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">▲土家族火塘。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">西汉时期，火塘、火墙、火炕仍然是普通百姓的不二选择。但或许是因为气候整体变暖，更为优雅和低碳的“温调房”得以出现在贵胄人家。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151004_859.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151004_859.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">▲花椒。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“温调房”关键材料是花椒，对，就是川菜必不可少那东西。当时人们就已经发现了它不仅食用可以除湿气，而且捣碎了和泥，涂在墙壁上同样可以释放其正能量，形成保温层。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_125.png\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_125.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">▲西汉椒房殿复原图。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">皇室的温调房则称为“温调殿”、“温室殿”、“温室”、“椒房殿”等。因为汉朝未央宫的椒房殿是皇后的居所，所以后来椒房也就成了后妃和后妃寝宫的代称。除了供人居住的温室外，汉代还有温室大棚，用于种植蔬菜。当时就有反季节蔬菜的说法，比如《盐铁论》里汉代富人吃的“冬葵”、“温韭”。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;\">暖手宝人人爱</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_234.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_234.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">▲火炕。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">相比于火坑、温室等大型的供暖设备，方便小巧的熏炉、手炉、汤婆子等也是居家必备，尤其是对于手冷、脚冷星人来说。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_330.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_330.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">▲沈阳故宫青宁宫西炕构造原理。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">熏炉就是白居易诗“绿蚁新醅酒，红泥小火炉”中的“红炉”，又称“暖炉”，是用陶土或者铜铁制成的贮火暖具，亦可以用于熏香，如李清照的“瑞脑销金兽”。而安徽寿县朱家集楚王墓出土的环链铜方炉则还具备了烧烤的功能，类似于一般人家的火盆。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_389.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_389.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">▲西晋青釉镂空三兽足熏炉。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_442.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_442.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">▲唐代被中香炉。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">还有一种球形的被中香炉，被设计成不论如何滚转，内部的炉口总是保持向上，因此可以睡觉时放在被中，而不必担心被烫伤。手炉则可以看成是熏炉的微缩版，炉外加罩，可以放在袖子里暖手。汤婆子是足炉的俗称，用锡或铜制成，内装热水，黄庭坚对此特别钟爱，“千钱买脚婆，夜夜睡天明”，显然是个脚冷星人。这三种可以直接接触皮肤，放在被子中的神器，无疑就是今日暖手宝、热水袋的鼻祖。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_642.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_642.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">▲明代脚炉。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_694.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151005_694.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">▲汤婆子。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151030_459.jpg\" alt=\"最强寒潮来袭：祖先们如何在北方的寒夜里四季如春？\" data-original=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_151030_459.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">▲手炉。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">正是有了这些大大小小的暖器，古人在极寒的天气里也可以四季如春。尽管如春的多是朱门，但是梁启超将暖气系列排除在“四大发明”之外，还是多少让我有些遗憾。后来发现，原来梁任公是广东人，他给自己的书斋起名叫饮冰室，又号饮冰子。</p>','2016-01-21 18:55:33',1,'00',1,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'http://sourceimg-10021396.image.myqcloud.com/680e05d2-6e8b-4dc0-9e9a-4731d3a8cf60'),(32,2,'Siri惹祸：苹果被起诉专利侵权','<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">北京时间1月21日消息，据科技博客AppleInsider报道，美国德克萨斯州专利授权公司Dot 23 Technologies将苹果告上法庭，指控<a class=\"s_tag\" href=\"http://iphone.ithome.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: text;\">iPhone</a>语音助手Siri的语音拨号和地理定位功能侵犯其三项专利权。Dot 23周三向德州东区地方法院提交了诉讼，指控苹果侵犯其三项专利权，这些专利涵盖了与Siri相关的多项智能机语音识别功能。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">苹果在2011年发布iPhone&nbsp;4s时一同推出了Siri语音助手。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2016/1/20160121_173656_550.jpg\" alt=\"Siri惹祸：苹果被起诉专利侵权\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 728px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">具体来说，这三项专利的专利号分别是6,917,802、7,245,903以及6,405,029，在2002年至2007年期间授予同一发明人布亚德·尼尔森(Byard G. Nilsson)。这三项专利全部被分配给了与尼尔森关联的有限责任公司Mobile Telephone Technology，去年9月被转让给了Dot 23。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“802”号和“029”号专利描述的都是通过中介程序执行基本语音拨号功能，该程序可以识别和处理口语字母数字式字符。目前，iPhone用户能够要求Siri逐个数字拨打电话号码，例如“拨打216-555-1234”。“093”号专利略有不同，它是根据要求基于地理位置相关的数据提供信息服务。例如，“加州北部哪里有中餐馆”。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1pc; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">除了Siri，Dot 23还将苹果iPhone 4、iPhone 5以及<a class=\"s_tag\" href=\"http://iphone.ithome.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); cursor: text;\">iPhone6</a>系列机型列为了侵权产品。Dot 23要求苹果作出赔偿。</p>','2016-01-21 18:56:35',1,'00',1,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,'http://sourceimg-10021396.image.myqcloud.com/680e05d2-6e8b-4dc0-9e9a-4731d3a8cf60'),(33,2,'很长很长的活动很长很长的活动很长很长的活动很长很长的活动很长很长的活动很长很长的活动很长很长的活动很长很长的活动','很长很长的活动很长很长的活动很长很长的活动很长很长的活动很长很长的活动很长很长的活动很长很长的活动<br><!-- 编辑区域 -->\n		    ','2016-01-22 12:12:55',1,'00',0,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,'http://sourceimg-10021396.image.myqcloud.com/680e05d2-6e8b-4dc0-9e9a-4731d3a8cf60'),(34,1,'很长很长的公告很长很长的公告很长很长的公告很长很长的公告很长很长的公告很长很长的公告很长很长的公告','很长很长的公告很长很长的公告很长很长的公告很长很长的公告很长很长的公告很长很长的公告很长很长的公告','2016-01-22 12:13:45',1,'00',1,5,NULL,NULL,NULL,'http://sourceimg-10021396.image.myqcloud.com/680e05d2-6e8b-4dc0-9e9a-4731d3a8cf60'),(35,2,'Tokenfield for Bootstrap','\n		    	<!-- 编辑区域 -->\n		    <pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 13px; white-space: nowrap; display: block; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; border-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: transparent;\"><code class=\"language-js\" data-lang=\"js\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, \'Courier N